<C>__{ethan}
<D>__{hello, aaron...}
<A>__{his eyes shift to martha and hold. ethan is, and always has been, in love with his brother's wife and she with him.}
<C>__{ethan}
<D>__{martha...}
<C>__{martha}
<P>__{(a bit shakily)}
<D>__{hello, ethan.}
<A>__{ethan slowly, stiffly swings out of the saddle. aaron and martha exchange quick glances... troubled, puzzled. aaron pastes on an uncertain smile as ethan comes around his horse toward their side.}
