<D>__{that old goat still creakin' around?... whyn't someone bury him?}
<A>__{he goes to his saddle pack, begins unlacing it. ben and debbie have inched closer half shy, half curious. debbie's dog begins sniffing at his heels. ethan looks down at them not unfriendly, just a man not used to children.}
